&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Field Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE JOB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Intro:&lt;/strong&gt; TurbineOne is a fast-moving and high-performance startup with a mission to strengthen situational awareness for all Americans serving at our nation’s frontlines - and we are backed by the best DefenseTech venture capitalists. Our Frontline Perception System is an edge-first software platform that allows anyone, even with no technical knowledge, to build and use machine learning models within a comms-contested tactical environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our rapidly growing startup seeks a talented and versatile Field Engineer to join our dynamic team. In this role, you&#39;ll be at the forefront of deploying our innovative ML solutions in high-stakes environments, working directly with national security customers to ensure seamless integration and optimal performance of our systems. As a crucial link between our development team and end-users, you&#39;ll have the opportunity to significantly impact national security operations while pushing the boundaries of ML technology. We want to hear from you if you thrive in fast-paced, challenging environments and are excited about the intersection of advanced technology and critical missions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Field Engineer&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reporting to: Engineering Operations Manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location:&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Geographically flexible for home-office with frequent travel required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be willing and able to travel up to 50% of the year.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand customer needs and requirements, providing tailored integration solutions using the Frontline Perception System (FPS).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and define integration processes for integrating FPS with existing and emergent systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write Software Scripts to enable system integrations and workarounds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with engineering, product, and customer success teams to deliver robust integration solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct on-site assessments and evaluations to understand customer infrastructure and recommend optimal integration strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop detailed integration plans, timelines, and documentation to guide the implementation process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide hands-on technical support and training to customers during the integration and deployment phases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously gather feedback from customers to iterate and improve integration processes and FPS capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure successful field deployments by troubleshooting and resolving integration issues promptly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On a Typical Day You Would:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provision and configure FPS deployments for each engagement you are assigned to.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet with customers to gather and understand their specific integration needs and constraints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and document a tailored integration process for the customer’s existing or emergent systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write a js or python script to route data generated in FPS to a client system via api subscription.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploy and configure FPS on-site, ensuring seamless integration with the customer’s infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical training and support to customer teams, ensuring they are confident in using FPS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams to refine and improve FPS based on field experiences and customer feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve any technical issues that arise during integration and deployment.&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Operations Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE JOB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Intro:&lt;/strong&gt; TurbineOne is a fast-moving and high-performance startup with a mission to strengthen situational awareness for all Americans serving at our nation’s frontlines - and we are backed by the best DefenseTech venture capitalists. Our Frontline Perception System is an edge-first software platform that allows anyone, even with no technical knowledge, to build and use machine learning models within a comms-contested tactical environment.&lt;/p&gt;
