&lt;p&gt;You will be a strategic guardian of our resources, helping us to balance flexibility and discipline as we transition into an institutional-grade defense-tech leader.&amp;nbsp; The ideal candidate is a team player with a “grab an oar” mentality and an ability to adapt and learn as the requirements of the role evolve.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
