&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE JOB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Intro: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.turbineone.com/&quot;&gt;TurbineOne&lt;/a&gt; is the frontline perception company. We deliver decision advantage, better situational awareness, and stronger force protection. Our customers love how we automate the right portions of the military intelligence cycle while keeping them in the loop. The company is a small, fast-moving, and high-performance startup that is backed by the best DefenseTech venture capitalists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‍&lt;/p&gt;
