&lt;li&gt;Partner with leadership to amplify executive and company presence online&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage targeted LinkedIn ad campaigns focused on defense, government, and enterprise buyers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop audience targeting strategies across military, federal, and industry communities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run testing across messaging, creative, and audience segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track campaign performance including engagement, CTR, conversions, and pipeline impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver performance insights and recommendations to leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support communications around major announcements, launches, and events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
