&lt;li&gt;Experience running LinkedIn advertising campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong writing and storytelling skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with paid digital campaigns and performance metrics&lt;/li&gt;
